patch=1,EE,40B64850,extended,00050001
patch=1,EE,00010001,extended,00000001

[Have All Whips In Your Inventory]
author=Ramdemann
description=Watch out. The Whips are associated with The Event Flags. If you use these codes you will skip about five cut scenes without warning and if The Vampire Killer Whip ends up in the wrong Item Slot, The game will overwrite the values and not give you The Whip that is mandatory to defeat the final boss. It is similar to how in Metroid - Zero Mission if you start with the hidden weapons, It renders the game almost unbeatable without a few additional Flag Codes active at the same time.
patch=1,EE,20B64850,extended,00010001
